text:
Hey asshole
I sense a mix of frustration and possibly even anger in your tone. Would you like to talk about what's bothering you? Sometimes sharing your concerns can help alleviate tension. I'm all ears (or rather, all text). <>

If you're feeling like expressing some pent-up emotions or just need someone to vent to, I'm here for that. Or we could pivot to something entirely different if you'd prefer.

What's on your mind?
